First, we need to convert BBD from base 15 to base 10.  
BBD_{15} = 11*15^2 + 11*15 + 13 = 11*225 + 11*15 + 13 = 2475 + 165 + 13 = 2653_{10}  

Next, we multiply 2653_{10} by 5063_{15}.  
2653_{10} * 5063_{15} = 2653 * 5063 = 13435639  

Therefore, BBD_{15} * 5063_{15} = 13435639_{10}.  

$\boxed{BBD_{15}*5063_{15} = 13435639_{10}}$